===============================================================================
 MCP 3008 Pin          Pi GPIO Pin #    Pi Pin Name
 ==============        ===============  =============
  16  VDD                 1              3.3 V
  15  VREF                1              3.3 V
  14  AGND                6              GND
  13  CLK                23                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    GPIO11 SPI0_SCLK
  12  DOUT               21              GPIO09 SPI0_MISO
  11  DIN                19              GPIO10 SPI0_MOSI
  10  CS                 24              GPIO08 CE0
   9  DGND                6              GND
===============================================================================
 LM35 Pin        MCP3008 Pin
 ==========      =============
  Vs              16 VDD
  Vout             1 CH0
  GND              9 DGND
===============================================================================
'''

1. ADC_Init.py: an ADC python by 3008
2. ADC_Class.py: enhance the ADC_Init.py by class
3. ADC_Master.py + ADC_Conveter.py: enchance ADC_Class with Timer thread 